Due to yesterdays failure to make a decent signature, I used the stock again and tried with different size. It looks alot better imo. [img]http://img503.imageshack.us/img503/2382/annasophiazi7.png[/img]
**Since other people fail to see it, and .Flair thinks he's king shit and makes fun of graphics that outwit him, I figure I should tell you what this picture actually it(I probably should have kept actual colors of the real-life objects) In the movie(s) I seen this character in, one of them she died, correct? If you pay attention to how I designed the background, it looks ALOT like clouds, right? I probably should have done it white/blue but it was too light for my taste. It shows that she had died and she is surrounded by clouds, and the sun shining on her forehead. Maybe I should change it so people stop saying shes 'retarded' and got 'down syndrome'.
